-- Barclays Makes 450 Million-Pound Hedging Provision
-- B y   H o w a r d   M u s t o e
-- 2012-07-27T06:27:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-27/barclays-makes-450-million-pound-hedging-provision-correct-.html
(Corrects to show provision was for interest rate
hedging.)  Barclays Plc (BARC)  said it added a 450
million-pound provision to redress customers sold interest rate
hedging products in the second quarter. The bank commented in a
statement today.  -- Editor: Jon Menon  To contact the reporter on this story:
